  "texts": [
    "In Section 5, the concepts of access control and authentication in relation to drones are presented.",
    "Section 6 summarizes the results and discussion.",
    "Section 7 summarizes the findings from the study and makes suggestions for further research.",
    "UAV networks are increasingly employed to transmit sensitive information in critical missions and applications.",
    "However, due to their limited computing and communication resources, anomalies and attacks pose a risk to the infrastructure of UAVs."
  ]
}